[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ふぁ～、今日もアトリエは平和だねぇ。\nみんな優しいし、すっかり居心地よくなっちゃったよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "リアス、あまり気を抜きすぎるなよ。\n油断してると、また何かやらかすんだから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "またってなによ！\nちょーっと、薬の瓶をひっくり返しただけじゃん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "その後、薬を被ったレスナさんに猫の耳が生えて\n大騒ぎになっただろ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ロゼ",
		"romanized_name": "Roze",
		"model_path_hash": "7640478782351486010",
		"text": "二人とも、やけに賑やかだな。\n痴話ゲンカはほどほどにしてくれ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "9196008292396767773",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ち、痴話ゲンカなんかじゃ……！\nって、あれ、ロジーだ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "久しぶりだな。元気にやっているようで何よりだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "疑似ガイストコアの調合、助かった。\nおかげで以前と変わらない感覚で戦えてる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "俺の知識が役に立ってよかったよ。\n興味深いからまた見させてくれ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ほんと、ありがとね！　あれがなかったら、\nあたしたち今頃どうなってたか……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "礼を言われるほどのことじゃないさ。\n俺も勉強になった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ロゼ",
		"romanized_name": "Roze",
		"model_path_hash": "7640478782351486010",
		"text": "まあ、ロジーはこう見えて腕は確かだからな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "9196008292396767773",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "そういえば、話に聞いたんだが……\nハルフェンには「亜空の道」というものがあるらしいな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ロゼ",
		"romanized_name": "Roze",
		"model_path_hash": "7640478782351486010",
		"text": "ああ、ロジーは知らないのか。簡単に言えば、\n遠く離れた場所までひとっ飛びできる特別な空間だな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "9196008292396767773",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "ひとっ飛びできる……？　\n転移装置のようなものか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "似たようなものかもしれない。\nだが、今はほとんど失われてしまった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "今残ってるのは、アルマの大樹の根っこに\n繋がってるやつだけだよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "新しく創ることはできないのか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "前にワルターが創ってくれたし、\nできるんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "いや……あの後詳しく聞かせてもらったんだが、\nどうも完全に新しいものではないらしい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "アルマの大樹の根に繋がる「亜空の道」を利用して、\n無理矢理横道と出入り口を創ったんだそうだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ロゼ",
		"romanized_name": "Roze",
		"model_path_hash": "7640478782351486010",
		"text": "同じようなやり方で出入り口を増やし続けたら、\n「亜空の道」の中はとんでもないことになるだろうな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "9196008292396767773",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "そうか……しかしすごい技術だな。もし再現できたら、\n各地の物流や人の移動も変わるだろうに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "ああ。いつかまた復活させてみたいな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]